name: Hiring Serpent
description:
Hi, I am Kiwi Kawaii   This artwork
depicts the day when the Forbidden
Tree from the Garden of Eden was
looking to hire a good and effective
serpent to tempt Eve to bite the
Forbidden fruit. Here, we can see
many of the serpents of that time,
each of them with with their own
personality, going to take a shot at the
interview and hopefully get the job.
